        <sect1>
            <title>House of Wihtgar</title>

            <para>
                Once a powerful House whose kings were part of the
                Council of Kings. It's lands were lost during the war
                with Merkia, and even the name of its old kingdom -
                that of Perrin - no longer exists. Today it is a weak
                house, dreaming of days gone by.
            </para>
        </sect1>
        
